dct_title_s: Delaware, Maryland, Virginia and West Virginia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "Copyright 1884 by Wm. M. Bradley & Bro." "61"--Upper right corner. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. Inset: [Hancock County]. Ancillary: Western part of Virginia. Probably issued in: Bradley's atlas of the world. Philadelphia, Wm. M. Bradley & Bros., c1884.
